01:31:34,074 --> 01:31:35,841
words, thoughts,
they had no impact?

1251
01:31:36,416 --> 01:31:38,543
What ideas? What thoughts?

1252
01:31:39,252 --> 01:31:40,913
There were only platitudes.

1253
01:31:40,987 --> 01:31:43,683
Nazi Germany was built
on empty platitudes.

1254
01:31:45,659 --> 01:31:49,618
A man like you, you were
seduced by empty platitudes?

1255
01:31:51,765 --> 01:31:52,823
Of course.

1256
01:31:52,966 --> 01:31:55,764
Because you can hear in
them any meaning you want.

1257
01:31:59,139 --> 01:32:01,573
You said earlier you wanted
to tell me something.

1258
01:32:05,946 --> 01:32:09,404
I've been trying to encourage
some of the other defendants...

1259
01:32:10,550 --> 01:32:13,849
to join with me in accepting
guilt and expressing remorse.

1260
01:32:14,521 --> 01:32:17,285
I made progress with Frank,
and I have had high hopes...

1261
01:32:17,357 --> 01:32:18,824
for young von Schirach.

1262
01:32:18,959 --> 01:32:21,826
But Göring means to bully
them into joining him.

1263
01:32:21,895 --> 01:32:24,159
And I fear now, he will succeed.

1264
01:32:24,931 --> 01:32:26,364
Unless someone stops him.

1265
01:32:28,368 --> 01:32:29,426
I understand.

1266
01:32:35,108 --> 01:32:36,268
All rise.

1267
01:32:58,331 --> 01:33:00,441
Herr Göring, do you
believe that the

1268
01:33:00,442 --> 01:33:02,495
Nazi party came
into power legally?

1269
01:33:03,069 --> 01:33:05,499
I do. And I am happy
to explain in detail

1270
01:33:05,500 --> 01:33:07,699
the history of those
first elections.

1271
01:33:07,974 --> 01:33:10,147
But I will add that
once we came to power,

1272
01:33:10,148 --> 01:33:12,070
we were determined
to hold onto it...

1273
01:33:12,145 --> 01:33:13,840
under all circumstances.

1274
01:33:14,114 --> 01:33:16,674
We did not want to leave
this any longer to chance...

1275
01:33:16,750 --> 01:33:19,048
to elections and
parliamentary majorities.

1276
01:33:19,285 --> 01:33:21,845
It had always been our plan
once we came to power...

1277
01:33:21,955 --> 01:33:24,116
that we would eliminate
the Reichstag...

1278
01:33:24,224 --> 01:33:27,318
dissolve the regional parliaments,
end individual rights.

1279
01:33:27,994 --> 01:33:29,933
Where did the idea
come from to combine

1280
01:33:29,934 --> 01:33:31,486
the ceremonial head of state...

1281
01:33:31,831 --> 01:33:34,959
and the head of government
in one person, Adolf Hitler?

1282
01:33:35,935 --> 01:33:37,770
That's quite simple. We took our

1283
01:33:37,771 --> 01:33:40,065
example from the
similar dual roles...

1284
01:33:40,140 --> 01:33:42,267
of the President of
the United States.

1285
01:33:45,779 --> 01:33:47,713
And the idea for
concentration camps?

1286
01:33:47,847 --> 01:33:49,109
The idea was mine.

1287
01:33:53,086 --> 01:33:55,054
It was a question
of removing danger.

1288
01:33:56,156 --> 01:33:58,021
Only one course was available.

1289
01:33:58,091 --> 01:33:59,490
Protective custody.

1290
01:33:59,926 --> 01:34:02,793
How could the party rule until
it had established order?

1291
01:34:03,129 --> 01:34:06,155
And how could it maintain order
with its deadly enemies...

1292
01:34:06,232 --> 01:34:08,723
particularly the
Communists, running free?

1293
01:34:13,907 --> 01:34:15,135
No further questions.

1294
01:34:31,091 --> 01:34:34,117
I don't get it. He's tightening
the noose around his own neck.

1295
01:34:34,194 --> 01:34:36,424
He doesn't care. He has
bigger fish to fry.

1296
01:34:36,496 --> 01:34:38,094
He's talking over the heads of the

1297
01:34:38,095 --> 01:34:40,023
tribunal directly to
the German people.

1298
01:34:40,100 --> 01:34:42,333
I suggest you isolate
him from the others

1299
01:34:42,334 --> 01:34:44,196
when they're not in the courtroom.

1300
01:34:52,679 --> 01:34:54,943
I don't understand. Why
are you doing this?

1301
01:34:55,381 --> 01:34:56,381
Inside.

1302
01:35:02,922 --> 01:35:04,981
Me? I'm just following orders.

1303
01:35:22,642 --> 01:35:23,666
During cross...

1304
01:35:23,743 --> 01:35:27,042
hit Göring quick and hard. Put
him on the defensive right away.

1305
01:35:27,113 --> 01:35:28,603
Never let him breathe.

1306
01:35:29,082 --> 01:35:30,802
I see no point in
that at all. He's

1307
01:35:30,803 --> 01:35:32,381
blatantly incriminating himself.

1308
01:35:32,952 --> 01:35:36,080
All I need to do is ask direct
questions and let him answer them.

1309
01:35:36,356 --> 01:35:39,120
Be prepared with a tough
line of questioning.

1310
01:35:39,459 --> 01:35:40,653
In case it's needed.

1311
01:35:42,595 --> 01:35:44,062
- Thank you.
- Sure.

1312
01:35:48,001 --> 01:35:50,265
Why am I being punished
like a schoolboy?

1313
01:35:51,204 --> 01:35:52,204
Speer?

1314
01:35:52,438 --> 01:35:53,803
Speer's behind this.

1315
01:35:54,007 --> 01:35:55,848
He must have talked
to Colonel Andrus,

1316
01:35:55,849 --> 01:35:57,738
persuaded him into
this line of action.

1317
01:35:57,810 --> 01:35:59,573
How do you know it wasn't me?

1318
01:36:00,413 --> 01:36:03,940
Why Dr Speer? Is there rivalry
between the two of you?

1319
01:36:04,017 --> 01:36:06,679
He is ashamed of being
a Nazi. I'm not.

1320
01:36:06,953 --> 01:36:09,217
He wishes to infect the
others with his shame.

1321
01:36:09,289 --> 01:36:10,688
You have no shame?

1322
01:36:11,291 --> 01:36:13,200
The world has now
seen proof of the

1323
01:36:13,201 --> 01:36:15,057
horrors committed by Nazi Germany.

1324
01:36:15,161 --> 01:36:17,095
You are comfortable defending it?

1325
01:36:17,163 --> 01:36:20,291
I've seen so many horrors already.
The carnage of the First War...

1326
01:36:20,366 --> 01:36:23,665
thousands of my countrymen
maimed, degraded, starved.

1327
01:36:25,071 --> 01:36:26,561
No, my dear doctor.

1328
01:36:27,040 --> 01:36:30,271
I am not an inhuman monster who
has no regard for human life.

1329
01:36:30,577 --> 01:36:33,341
These atrocities are
not indifferent to me.

1330
01:36:35,148 --> 01:36:38,515
You know, we are accused of
so many appalling acts...

1331
01:36:38,718 --> 01:36:40,208
it is hard to keep track.

1332
01:36:40,653 --> 01:36:43,019
- Did you try?
- My concern was war.

1333
01:36:43,523 --> 01:36:46,151
And in war, each nation has
its own selfish interest.

1334
01:36:46,826 --> 01:36:48,293
You have to be practical.

1335
01:36:48,795 --> 01:36:52,094
I am a practical man.
And I'm a soldier.

1336
01:36:52,765 --> 01:36:54,858
And a soldier's code is obedience.

1337
01:36:56,536 --> 01:36:57,536
Obedience.

1338
01:36:57,570 --> 01:36:59,094
This amuses you?

1339
01:36:59,572 --> 01:37:01,836
Blind obedience without
responsibility.

1340
01:37:01,908 --> 01:37:03,705
Is there nobody in this country...

1341
01:37:03,810 --> 01:37:07,746
that will take responsibility for
anything? Nobody who can say no?

1342
01:37:07,814 --> 01:37:11,045
Take a look at every cell in
this block. What do you see?

1343
01:37:11,484 --> 01:37:12,484
Yes men.

1344
01:37:13,019 --> 01:37:15,112
All the no men are six
feet underground.

1345
01:37:18,658 --> 01:37:19,818
What is this?

1346
01:37:22,495 --> 01:37:24,190
You're not Jewish, are you?

1347
01:37:29,135 --> 01:37:30,966
Yes. I am.

1348
01:37:37,076 --> 01:37:38,304
I see.

1349
01:37:41,714 --> 01:37:44,012
This is a very
interesting situation.

1350
01:37:44,951 --> 01:37:46,248
For both of us.

1351
01:38:01,301 --> 01:38:02,700
Good luck, old boy.

1352
01:38:06,072 --> 01:38:07,505
So, what's his plan?

1353
01:38:08,174 --> 01:38:09,573
I haven't a clue.

1354
01:38:16,182 --> 01:38:18,343
Will the witness repeat
this oath after me?

1355
01:38:20,420 --> 01:38:22,888
"I swear by God the
Almighty and Omniscient..."

1356
01:38:23,589 --> 01:38:25,921
I swear by God the
Almighty and Omniscient...

1357
01:38:26,125 --> 01:38:28,491
"that I will speak
the pure truth...

1358
01:38:28,628 --> 01:38:30,755
"and will withhold
and add nothing."

1359
01:38:30,997 --> 01:38:34,694
That I will speak the pure truth
and will withhold and add nothing.

1360
01:38:37,070 --> 01:38:38,469
Mr Chief Prosecutor?

1361
01:38:54,120 --> 01:38:57,283
You are perhaps aware that you
are the only living man...

1362
01:38:57,657 --> 01:38:59,215
who can expound to us...

1363
01:38:59,292 --> 01:39:01,444
the true purposes of
the Nazi Party and

1364
01:39:01,445 --> 01:39:03,490
the inner workings
of its leadership.

1365
01:39:03,663 --> 01:39:05,221
I am perfectly aware of that.

1366
01:39:05,298 --> 01:39:06,959
You, from the very beginning...

1367
01:39:07,033 --> 01:39:10,298
together with those who you
were associated with...

1368
01:39:10,870 --> 01:39:13,566
intended to overthrow, and
later on did overthrow...

1369
01:39:13,973 --> 01:39:17,170
Germany's previous government,
the Weimar Republic?

1370
01:39:17,243 --> 01:39:18,870
That was my firm intention.

1371
01:39:19,112 --> 01:39:20,854
And upon coming to power you

1372
01:39:20,855 --> 01:39:23,344
immediately abolished
parliamentary...

1373
01:39:23,683 --> 01:39:25,548
democratic government in Germany.

1374
01:39:26,152 --> 01:39:28,120
We found it no longer
to be necessary.

1375
01:39:28,521 --> 01:39:31,285
Is it not true that people
were subsequently thrown...

1376
01:39:31,357 --> 01:39:34,554
into concentration camps without
recourse from the courts?

1377
01:39:34,627 --> 01:39:37,187
You must distinguish
between two categories.

1378
01:39:37,764 --> 01:39:40,733
Those who had committed a treason
against the new state...

1379
01:39:40,933 --> 01:39:42,560
were turned over to the courts.

1380
01:39:42,635 --> 01:39:44,865
Others, of whom one might
expect such acts...

1381
01:39:44,937 --> 01:39:46,700
but who had not yet
committed them...

1382
01:39:46,773 --> 01:39:49,241
such as functionaries of
the Communist Party...

1383
01:39:49,308 --> 01:39:50,707
who were attacking us...

1384
01:39:50,777 --> 01:39:52,176
You answered the question.

1385
01:39:52,378 --> 01:39:53,845
I need to explain further.

1386
01:39:53,913 --> 01:39:56,040
You'll have the
opportunity to explain...

1387
01:39:56,115 --> 01:39:58,379
under re-examination
from your own counsel.

1388
01:39:59,886 --> 01:40:04,016
Did you prohibit all court review
of the cause for taking people...

1389
01:40:04,090 --> 01:40:06,684
into what you were calling
"protective custody"?

1390
01:40:06,759 --> 01:40:09,990
That I answered very clearly, but
I'd like to make an explanation...

1391
01:40:10,062 --> 01:40:11,290
about my answer.

1392
01:40:11,364 --> 01:40:13,855
Your counsel will see to
that. About the camps...

1393
01:40:13,933 --> 01:40:15,423
Mr Justice Jackson.

1394
01:40:15,501 --> 01:40:18,334
The Tribunal thinks the witness
must be allowed to make...

1395
01:40:18,438 --> 01:40:21,464
what explanation he thinks right
in answer to this question.

1396
01:40:28,247 --> 01:40:30,715
The Tribunal thinks that
you should be permitted...

1397
01:40:30,817 --> 01:40:32,648
to explain your answer now...

1398
01:40:32,718 --> 01:40:35,278
and it will listen
to that explanation.

1399
01:40:38,958 --> 01:40:40,983
I want to say that I
issued a decree...

1400
01:40:41,060 --> 01:40:44,120
that those who were turned over
to the concentration camps...

1401
01:40:44,430 --> 01:40:48,093
should be informed after
24 hours of the reason...

1402
01:40:48,768 --> 01:40:50,929
and allowed an attorney
after 48 hours.

1403
01:40:51,003 --> 01:40:54,461
This by no means rescinded my
order that a court review...

1404
01:40:54,540 --> 01:40:56,599
of these measures
was not permitted.

1405
01:40:56,676 --> 01:40:58,507
By "protective
custody" you mean...

1406
01:40:58,578 --> 01:41:01,672
taking people in custody who had
not yet committed a crime...

1407
01:41:01,747 --> 01:41:04,238
but you believed might commit
a crime in the future?

1408
01:41:04,317 --> 01:41:06,366
Yes, just as extensive
protective measures

1409
01:41:06,367 --> 01:41:08,083
are being taken in
Germany today...

1410
01:41:08,187 --> 01:41:10,553
I didn't ask you
about Germany today.

1411
01:41:10,656 --> 01:41:11,953
Mr Justice Jackson.

1412
01:41:12,158 --> 01:41:13,785
This is poor preparation.

1413
01:41:16,496 --> 01:41:19,090
The witness may finish
his explanation.

1414
01:41:33,980 --> 01:41:36,813
You say that you were against
the attack on Soviet Russia.

1415
01:41:37,116 --> 01:41:40,017
Yet you gave no warning
to the German people.

1416
01:41:40,553 --> 01:41:42,817
You brought no pressure
to bear to prevent it.

1417
01:41:43,089 --> 01:41:45,717
You did not even resign to
protect your place in history.

1418
01:41:45,791 --> 01:41:47,585
We were at war, and
such differences

1419
01:41:47,586 --> 01:41:49,283
of opinion could not be brought...

1420
01:41:49,362 --> 01:41:51,387
before the public during war.

1421
01:41:51,464 --> 01:41:53,295
This was the case in
your own country.

1422
01:41:53,366 --> 01:41:55,129
- Your second question...
- That'll suffice.

1423
01:41:55,201 --> 01:41:56,862
I'm not finished. Secondly...

1424
01:41:56,936 --> 01:41:57,936
Your Honour, please.

1425
01:41:57,937 --> 01:42:00,395
The witness must be
allowed to have his say.

1426
01:42:01,607 --> 01:42:03,575
As far as my resignation...

1427
01:42:03,643 --> 01:42:05,941
I do not wish even
to discuss that...

1428
01:42:06,245 --> 01:42:08,543
for I was an officer, a soldier.

1429
01:42:08,948 --> 01:42:10,381
I served my country.

1430
01:42:10,449 --> 01:42:11,473
- I ask you...
- Thirdly...

1431
01:42:11,551 --> 01:42:12,551
Your Honour, please.

1432
01:42:12,618 --> 01:42:13,618
Thirdly...

1433
01:42:13,619 --> 01:42:16,044
I was not the man to
forsake someone...

1434
01:42:16,122 --> 01:42:18,352
to whom I had given
my oath of loyalty...

1435
01:42:18,424 --> 01:42:20,688
every time he was not
to my way of thinking.

1436
01:42:20,760 --> 01:42:21,760
Your Honour...

1437
01:42:21,761 --> 01:42:24,758
It never, ever occurred to
me to leave the Führer.

1438
01:42:26,966 --> 01:42:29,434
The witness is adopting a
contemptuous attitude...

1439
01:42:29,502 --> 01:42:30,560
toward this Tribunal...

1440
01:42:30,636 --> 01:42:33,901
which is giving him trial that
he never gave a living soul...

1441
01:42:33,973 --> 01:42:35,372
nor dead ones either.

1442
01:42:35,441 --> 01:42:37,170
Objection, Your Honour.

1443
01:42:43,115 --> 01:42:44,878
I'm ready for the next question.

1444
01:42:56,062 --> 01:42:59,122
I think this is probably a good
point to adjourn for the day.

1445
01:43:24,790 --> 01:43:26,382
Tough calls from the bench.

1446
01:43:26,993 --> 01:43:28,620
Well, it's only Round One.

1447
01:43:29,662 --> 01:43:32,426
If you think you need anything,
don't forget, I'm here.

1448
01:43:58,190 --> 01:44:01,318
As the week ends, there's a
consensus among all present...

1449
01:44:01,494 --> 01:44:04,895
that Hermann Göring now appears
to be in control of the court.

1450
01:44:05,431 --> 01:44:09,197
Will Jackson? Will anyone
be able to stop him?

1451
01:44:13,305 --> 01:44:14,305
Yes, Bob?

1452
01:44:17,543 --> 01:44:20,944
You know, Judge, I didn't leave
the Supreme Court to come here...

1453
01:44:21,013 --> 01:44:23,243
and be thwarted by a
fellow countrymen.

1454
01:44:23,883 --> 01:44:26,681
That sounds like sour
grapes. Very unbecoming.

1455
01:44:26,986 --> 01:44:29,144
To an outsider, it
might appear like

1456
01:44:29,145 --> 01:44:31,013
you were trying to sabotage me.

1457
01:44:31,891 --> 01:44:35,827
You gave Göring an open forum
during direct examination.

1458
01:44:35,895 --> 01:44:38,090
I must be able to control
him during cross.

1459
01:44:39,632 --> 01:44:41,410
Just accept the fact
that you weren't

1460
01:44:41,411 --> 01:44:42,863
at the top of your game today.

1461
01:44:43,703 --> 01:44:46,171
You have the weekend to
prepare for the next round.

1462
01:44:46,872 --> 01:44:48,100
Make good use of it.

1463
01:45:20,239 --> 01:45:22,901
- Not hungry, sir?
- I'm too excited to eat.

1464
01:45:25,411 --> 01:45:26,935
Did you hear what I said?

1465
01:45:27,179 --> 01:45:29,773
My reply when he asked
me why I did not resign?

1466
01:45:30,349 --> 01:45:31,941
I lectured him about loyalty.

1467
01:45:32,051 --> 01:45:34,144
You should have seen
Jackson's face.

1468
01:45:34,887 --> 01:45:37,378
It was a completely
foreign concept to him.

1469
01:45:37,456 --> 01:45:40,323
If I didn't know better, I
would say Jackson was a Jew.

1470
01:45:41,594 --> 01:45:42,788
No. Keep it.

1471
01:45:44,497 --> 01:45:46,692
My initials, see? Engraved.

1472
01:45:47,800 --> 01:45:49,062
It's real nice.

1473
01:45:50,669 --> 01:45:51,727
I'll never forget this.

1474
01:45:51,804 --> 01:45:53,431
I know, Leutnant. I know.

1475
01:45:54,306 --> 01:45:55,534
Sit down.

1476
01:45:56,809 --> 01:46:00,142
You know, my friends call me Tex.

1477
01:46:01,413 --> 01:46:03,005
All right, Tex.

1478
01:46:03,783 --> 01:46:05,978
Let me tell you something, Tex.

1479
01:46:06,051 --> 01:46:09,384
America will soon learn that they
are backing the wrong philosophy.

1480
01:46:09,455 --> 01:46:12,322
We should both be together
fighting the forces of Communism.

1481
01:46:13,092 --> 01:46:14,320
- You think?
- Yeah.

1482
01:46:15,161 --> 01:46:16,253
You think?

1483
01:46:16,495 --> 01:46:17,621
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

1484
01:46:18,297 --> 01:46:20,322
- I think we both agree, no?
- Yeah.

1485
01:46:26,138 --> 01:46:28,003
I'd like to dictate a telegram.

1486
01:46:37,950 --> 01:46:39,815
President Truman, the White House.

1487
01:46:39,885 --> 01:46:41,881
"Please accept my
resignation as Chief

1488
01:46:41,882 --> 01:46:43,878
Prosecutor for the
Nuremberg trials...

1489
01:46:44,290 --> 01:46:47,157
"and appoint a replacement
at the earliest possible..."

1490
01:46:47,693 --> 01:46:50,253
I'm not writing this. I won't.

1491
01:46:53,566 --> 01:46:56,592
You saw today that I'm
not up to this task.

1492
01:46:56,902 --> 01:47:01,100
I could stay, out of pride,
and unravel everything...

1493
01:47:01,173 --> 01:47:04,370
we've all worked so hard
for. Or I can step aside...

1494
01:47:04,443 --> 01:47:06,070
Bob, you are this trial.

1495
01:47:06,412 --> 01:47:09,848
Everything it is, everything it
represents, is from inside you.

1496
01:47:09,915 --> 01:47:11,746
Your thoughts, your values.

1497
01:47:11,851 --> 01:47:13,716
I tasted failure today...

1498
01:47:14,453 --> 01:47:17,251
and realised what it would
mean. Not only to myself...

1499
01:47:17,323 --> 01:47:19,348
but to everyone
connected with this.

1500
01:47:19,425 --> 01:47:21,825
The only way they can
triumph over you...

1501
01:47:21,894 --> 01:47:24,192
is if their values are
stronger than yours.

1502
01:47:24,363 --> 01:47:27,662
If they believe in their ideals
more than you believe in yours.

1503
01:47:29,368 --> 01:47:30,528
Is that true, Bob?

1504
01:47:32,304 --> 01:47:34,864
Does Hermann Göring actually
believe in his ideals...

1505
01:47:34,940 --> 01:47:37,033
more than you believe in yours?

1506
01:48:10,342 --> 01:48:11,673
You're right.

1507
01:48:13,946 --> 01:48:14,946
And thank you.

1508
01:48:26,792 --> 01:48:28,020
You're welcome.

1509
01:48:58,390 --> 01:49:01,951
Now, look here. What happened
wasn't entirely your fault.

1510
01:49:03,128 --> 01:49:06,120
God knows, I'd be hard-pressed
to defeat a clever defendant...

1511
01:49:06,198 --> 01:49:09,690
who's allowed to say whatever he
wants for as long as he wants.

1512
01:49:10,302 --> 01:49:13,533
Now that you've finished with the
niceties, let's have the truth.

1513
01:49:14,540 --> 01:49:17,566
Well, it was very
damaging, Robert.

1514
01:49:19,144 --> 01:49:22,272
You've introduced this trial from
a position of moral superiority.

1515
01:49:22,548 --> 01:49:25,142
And as a result, you've
become its chief symbol.

1516
01:49:25,918 --> 01:49:27,476
If you can't maintain that...

1517
01:49:27,553 --> 01:49:30,784
or if the balance shifts ever so
slightly it could be a disaster.

1518
01:49:31,690 --> 01:49:33,783
Hermann Göring is
using this trial...

1519
01:49:33,993 --> 01:49:35,276
to present himself as a

1520
01:49:35,277 --> 01:49:37,622
philosopher-statesman
on Hitler's level.

1521
01:49:38,330 --> 01:49:40,127
Do you see Göring as a statesman?

1522
01:49:40,466 --> 01:49:43,993
No, I do not. I see
him as reprehensible.

1523
01:49:44,837 --> 01:49:45,997
As inhuman.

1524
01:49:46,071 --> 01:49:47,402
Then treat him as such.

1525
01:49:47,673 --> 01:49:49,766
Treat him as the
vile, conniving...

1526
01:49:49,842 --> 01:49:52,174
bloody fascist bastard that he is.

1527
01:50:04,390 --> 01:50:05,618
Where the hell is he?

1528
01:50:05,691 --> 01:50:06,885
He'll be here.

1529
01:50:33,352 --> 01:50:35,980
Mr Chief Prosecutor,
if you are ready.

1530
01:50:36,889 --> 01:50:38,705
From the very
beginning, you regarded

1531
01:50:38,706 --> 01:50:40,188
the elimination of the Jews...

1532
01:50:40,259 --> 01:50:42,183
from the economic
life of Germany as

1533
01:50:42,184 --> 01:50:44,161
under your jurisdiction,
did you not?

1534
01:50:44,496 --> 01:50:46,530
Yeah. The elimination
from economic

1535
01:50:46,531 --> 01:50:48,227
life, that is partly correct.

1536
01:50:48,934 --> 01:50:52,961
Large industries, also armament
industries under Jewish directors.

1537
01:50:53,305 --> 01:50:56,172
Was that the first of your legal
measures against the Jews?

1538
01:50:56,241 --> 01:50:58,766
I believe removal from
office was first, in 1933.

1539
01:50:59,011 --> 01:51:02,879
Then, in 1936, you
personally drafted an act...

1540
01:51:03,315 --> 01:51:06,773
making it punishable by death
to transfer property abroad?

1541
01:51:06,919 --> 01:51:08,011
That is correct.

1542
01:51:08,087 --> 01:51:11,784
And another that all damage
caused to Jewish property...

1543
01:51:12,324 --> 01:51:14,792
by the anti-Jewish
riots of 1938...

1544
01:51:14,927 --> 01:51:17,418
must be repaired by Jews
at their own expense...

1545
01:51:17,996 --> 01:51:21,056
with their insurance claims
forfeited to the Reich.

1546
01:51:21,567 --> 01:51:24,661
I did sign a similar law. Whether
it was exactly the same, I...

1547
01:51:25,204 --> 01:51:27,695
And did you not say
about those riots...

1548
01:51:28,907 --> 01:51:30,670
I show you this transcript.

1549
01:51:32,277 --> 01:51:35,804
Did you not say, "I wish
you had killed 200 Jews...

1550
01:51:36,048 --> 01:51:38,209
"instead of destroying
such valuables"?

1551
01:51:38,484 --> 01:51:41,715
That was said in a moment of bad
temper and extreme excitement.

1552
01:51:41,954 --> 01:51:44,354
Spontaneous sincerity,
in other words.

1553
01:51:45,357 --> 01:51:48,952
Did you not also personally sign
a decree in September, 1940...

1554
01:51:49,128 --> 01:51:51,688
ordering seizure of all
Jewish property in Poland?

1555
01:51:51,930 --> 01:51:53,693
I assume so, if the
decree is there.

1556
01:51:53,765 --> 01:51:56,928
And another, which provided that
Jews receive no compensation...

1557
01:51:57,002 --> 01:52:01,098
for damages caused by enemy
attacks or by German forces?

1558
01:52:01,173 --> 01:52:03,403
If the law bears my name,
then it must be so.

1559
01:52:06,578 --> 01:52:07,943
Is this your signature?

1560
01:52:09,748 --> 01:52:10,806
It appears to be.

1561
01:52:10,883 --> 01:52:13,681
Is it, or is it not,
your signature?

1562
01:52:21,160 --> 01:52:22,160
It is.

1563
01:52:23,462 --> 01:52:25,089
Your signature...

1564
01:52:25,597 --> 01:52:29,829
on a decree dated July,
1941 asking Himmler...

1565
01:52:30,602 --> 01:52:33,093
and Heydrich and the
SS to make plans...

1566
01:52:33,338 --> 01:52:35,806
for the "final solution"
of the Jewish question.

1567
01:52:35,874 --> 01:52:37,933
That is not a proper translation.

1568
01:52:39,278 --> 01:52:41,746
I said "total" solution,
not "final" solution.

1569
01:52:41,813 --> 01:52:43,872
These are your words to Himmler:

1570
01:52:44,416 --> 01:52:47,715
"I charge you to send me before
long an overall plan concerning...

1571
01:52:47,819 --> 01:52:51,016
"the organisational, factual and
material measures necessary...

1572
01:52:51,356 --> 01:52:53,984
"for the desired solution
of the Jewish question."

1573
01:52:55,160 --> 01:52:57,076
Is that an accurate
translation of this

1574
01:52:57,077 --> 01:52:58,994
order from you to
Heydrich and Himmler?

1575
01:52:59,064 --> 01:53:02,056
That had to do with emigration
and evacuation of the Jews.

1576
01:53:02,334 --> 01:53:04,131
You ordered all
government agencies

1577
01:53:04,132 --> 01:53:05,531
to cooperate with the SS...

1578
01:53:05,604 --> 01:53:07,868
in the final solution
of the Jewish question.

1579
01:53:08,273 --> 01:53:10,104
There's nothing in
there about the SS.

1580
01:53:10,175 --> 01:53:11,962
This document states
you personally

1581
01:53:11,963 --> 01:53:13,702
ordered all government agencies...

1582
01:53:13,779 --> 01:53:15,371
to cooperate with the SS.

1583
01:53:15,781 --> 01:53:18,306
You sent this letter to SS
Gruppenführer Heydrich.

1584
01:53:18,383 --> 01:53:19,937
That doesn't mean that the SS had

1585
01:53:19,938 --> 01:53:21,682
anything to do with
the solution...

1586
01:53:21,753 --> 01:53:23,380
to the Jewish question.

1587
01:53:33,377 --> 01:53:34,844
I must say this clearly.

1588
01:53:38,349 --> 01:53:40,613
I did not know anything
that took place...

1589
01:53:41,518 --> 01:53:45,181
or the methods that were used in
the concentration camps later.

1590
01:53:45,956 --> 01:53:48,220
These things were
kept secret from me.

1591
01:53:49,693 --> 01:53:51,058
And I might add...

1592
01:53:51,795 --> 01:53:53,524
that in my opinion...

1593
01:53:53,697 --> 01:53:56,825
even the Führer did not know the
extent of what was happening.

1594
01:54:03,841 --> 01:54:06,275
Witness, there is evidence
before this court...

1595
01:54:06,343 --> 01:54:09,141
that nearly 10 million people
have been exterminated.

1596
01:54:10,281 --> 01:54:11,771
Murdered in cold blood.

1597
01:54:11,849 --> 01:54:13,648
You mean to say that
you did not, and

1598
01:54:13,649 --> 01:54:15,307
in your opinion, Hitler did not...

1599
01:54:15,386 --> 01:54:17,854
know what took place in
the concentration camps?

1600
01:54:20,658 --> 01:54:21,658
Yeah.

1601
01:54:23,928 --> 01:54:26,294
Do you know that
Hitler said in 1943...

1602
01:54:26,964 --> 01:54:30,024
in a recorded meeting, I
read you his words now.

1603
01:54:30,100 --> 01:54:33,126
Quote: "The Reich's Minister
of Foreign Affairs...

1604
01:54:33,237 --> 01:54:36,001
"declared that the Jews
should be exterminated...

1605
01:54:37,207 --> 01:54:39,175
"or taken to concentration camps.

1606
01:54:41,178 --> 01:54:43,078
"There is no other possibility."

1607
01:54:44,114 --> 01:54:47,083
The Minister of Foreign
Affairs, Ribbentrop...

1608
01:54:47,751 --> 01:54:49,912
talked with Hitler
about extermination.

1609
01:54:49,987 --> 01:54:52,581
And you were above Ribbentrop.

1610
01:54:52,723 --> 01:54:54,714
You were Hitler's
second-in-command.

1611
01:54:54,892 --> 01:54:57,588
You were in charge of the
economic Four Year Plan...

1612
01:54:57,661 --> 01:55:00,129
so you knew all about the
gold wedding rings...

1613
01:55:00,197 --> 01:55:02,382
the gold teeth and
the gold eyeglasses

1614
01:55:02,383 --> 01:55:04,065
that the victims left behind.

1615
01:55:04,368 --> 01:55:07,428
And you have heard that it
took five extra minutes...

1616
01:55:07,538 --> 01:55:10,598
to kill the women because they
had to cut their hair off...

1617
01:55:10,674 --> 01:55:13,040
to be used in making mattresses.

1618
01:55:13,677 --> 01:55:16,544
And nothing was told to you...

1619
01:55:16,613 --> 01:55:18,326
about this material that came from

1620
01:55:18,327 --> 01:55:20,242
these people that
had been murdered?

1621
01:55:20,484 --> 01:55:21,484
No.

1622
01:55:23,821 --> 01:55:24,821
No.

1623
01:55:26,357 --> 01:55:28,450
How can you imagine such a thing?

1624
01:55:31,495 --> 01:55:35,261
I was laying down the broad
outlines of the German economy.

1625
01:55:38,736 --> 01:55:40,897
- The witness is excused.
- I'm not finished.

1626
01:55:40,971 --> 01:55:43,201
- The witness is excused.
- I am not finished.

1627
01:55:43,941 --> 01:55:45,875
The witness is excused.

1628
01:56:23,514 --> 01:56:25,379
You know what would've
been a great touch?

1629
01:56:25,449 --> 01:56:27,883
Hermann Göring showing
up in a Santa outfit.

1630
01:56:28,919 --> 01:56:30,386
He'd probably do it.

1631
01:56:30,454 --> 01:56:33,321
After all, he was the Third
Reich's chief bon vivant.

1632
01:56:33,390 --> 01:56:36,484
Did you ever see pictures of him
at Hitler's mountain retreat...

1633
01:56:36,560 --> 01:56:38,462
dressed like a
Tyrollean chorus boy

1634
01:56:38,463 --> 01:56:40,155
out of some grotesque operetta?

1635
01:56:52,476 --> 01:56:53,476
Excuse me.

1636
01:56:58,282 --> 01:56:59,408
Leaving so soon?

1637
01:56:59,883 --> 01:57:02,374
Some of the defendants asked
me to come by tonight.

1638
01:57:02,453 --> 01:57:04,785
A little Christmas Eve
chat with their rabbi.

1639
01:57:07,858 --> 01:57:09,704
You know the trial
is about to enter

1640
01:57:09,705 --> 01:57:11,453
a new phase, a very important one.

1641
01:57:11,528 --> 01:57:13,586
The defendants will have to choose

1642
01:57:13,587 --> 01:57:15,828
between stonewalling
and evading...

1643
01:57:15,933 --> 01:57:18,265
or taking responsibility
for their actions.

1644
01:57:18,335 --> 01:57:23,796
Now, you are the best chance we
have to influence that choice.

1645
01:57:42,893 --> 01:57:43,893
Frau Hassel?

1646
01:57:44,862 --> 01:57:46,090
Is something wrong?

1647
01:57:46,396 --> 01:57:48,830
Do not ask me to serve
the Russians. Please.

1648
01:57:49,233 --> 01:57:50,427
They're our guests.

1649
01:57:51,502 --> 01:57:53,629
My son was killed on
the Russian front.

1650
01:57:55,606 --> 01:57:58,040
Okay. I'll take care of
this. Go to the kitchen.

1651
01:58:03,247 --> 01:58:05,511
Try these little sausage
things, General.

1652
01:58:05,582 --> 01:58:07,401
I forget what Frau
Hassel calls them,

1653
01:58:07,402 --> 01:58:08,983
but I hear they're mighty tasty.

1654
01:58:10,220 --> 01:58:11,220
Madame.

1655
01:58:11,889 --> 01:58:14,983
20 million of my people
were killed by the Germans.

1656
01:58:16,460 --> 01:58:19,293
Do you think I could be offended
by the snub of a Hausfrau?

1657
01:58:20,230 --> 01:58:22,095
I don't know what
to think, General.

1658
01:58:22,166 --> 01:58:25,101
Frankly, I can't keep track of
all the politics in this room.

1659
01:58:39,049 --> 01:58:41,677
The Russians sure don't
disappear in a crowd, do they?

1660
01:58:41,818 --> 01:58:42,978
Politics.

1661
01:58:43,787 --> 01:58:47,052
They've suffered more in this
war than any other country.

1662
01:58:47,691 --> 01:58:51,024
Must be doubly painful to attract
such little sympathy for them.

1663
01:58:58,969 --> 01:59:02,097
And Jackson decreed no
wives could come along.

1664
01:59:05,742 --> 01:59:08,210
Worked out quite nicely for
him, wouldn't you say?

1665
01:59:54,891 --> 01:59:56,153
Merry Christmas.

1666
02:01:00,490 --> 02:01:02,355
This was a very nice gesture.

1667
02:01:05,996 --> 02:01:08,464
I figured it's probably
their last Christmas.

1668
02:01:16,506 --> 02:01:18,064
Merry Christmas, Colonel.

1669
02:01:31,355 --> 02:01:33,220
- Field Marshal.
- Doctor.

1670
02:01:33,490 --> 02:01:34,514
How are you?

1671
02:01:34,991 --> 02:01:36,720
I'm so glad that you are here.

1672
02:01:37,527 --> 02:01:41,224
Please, sit. You are the only
one I can really talk to.

1673
02:01:42,132 --> 02:01:45,693
But you don't talk to me,
Field Marshal. Not really.

1674
02:01:46,603 --> 02:01:48,496
I tell you everything
about my family.

1675
02:01:48,497 --> 02:01:49,497
Yes.

1676
02:01:49,498 --> 02:01:50,839
But not about you.

1677
02:01:52,509 --> 02:01:55,137
I would like to understand
how a man like you...

1678
02:01:55,212 --> 02:01:56,839
a man of your background...

1679
02:01:56,913 --> 02:02:00,280
could have drafted an instrument
like the Commando Order.

1680
02:02:00,884 --> 02:02:03,910
Allied soldiers found behind
enemy lines were shot...

1681
02:02:04,254 --> 02:02:05,653
rather than captured?

1682
02:02:05,856 --> 02:02:08,723
Or the Night and Fog Decree:
Suspected Resistance members...

1683
02:02:08,792 --> 02:02:12,057
were arrested in the middle of
the night and secretly murdered.

1684
02:02:14,631 --> 02:02:15,928
Because of you.

1685
02:02:19,636 --> 02:02:22,571
I know. I am dying of shame.

1686
02:02:26,109 --> 02:02:27,965
Don't you think it's
time you admitted

1687
02:02:27,966 --> 02:02:29,442
that to the rest of the world?

1688
02:02:57,674 --> 02:03:00,370
I'm not in the mood, all right.

1689
02:03:01,044 --> 02:03:02,136
Get off me.

1690
02:03:02,212 --> 02:03:03,212
Get off.

1691
02:03:21,164 --> 02:03:24,361
You were signing orders that broke
international laws and treaties.

1692
02:03:24,434 --> 02:03:26,561
How could you not question
what you were doing?

1693
02:03:26,636 --> 02:03:28,488
Does a lieutenant
say to his captain,

1694
02:03:28,489 --> 02:03:30,538
"Just a minute, sir,
I have to consult...

1695
02:03:30,607 --> 02:03:32,594
"the Hague Convention
to see if I am

1696
02:03:32,595 --> 02:03:34,475
allowed to carry out your orders?"

1697
02:03:35,145 --> 02:03:37,613
If we had disobeyed, we
would have been arrested.

1698
02:03:37,681 --> 02:03:38,681
Rightly so.

1699
02:03:38,682 --> 02:03:41,674
You realise without the support
of his generals, Herr Jodl...

1700
02:03:41,751 --> 02:03:43,651
Hitler could not have waged war.

1701
02:03:43,920 --> 02:03:47,515
It is a soldier's duty
is to obey orders.

1702
02:03:48,358 --> 02:03:50,849
That is a code I have
lived by all my life.

1703
02:03:50,961 --> 02:03:53,828
And that code extends to the
people who ran the death camps?

1704
02:04:27,230 --> 02:04:28,254
I'm sorry, sir.

1705
02:04:29,065 --> 02:04:32,228
Tex, my friend. Come in.

1706
02:04:33,537 --> 02:04:35,232
- Sit down.
- Thank you.

1707
02:04:35,305 --> 02:04:36,602
It's good to see you.

1708
02:04:38,308 --> 02:04:42,267
I know that Christmastime can be
a lonely thing away from home.

1709
02:04:43,780 --> 02:04:45,543
Merry Christmas, Reichsmarschall.

1710
02:04:45,615 --> 02:04:48,641
My dear Tex, what luxury.

1711
02:04:52,589 --> 02:04:53,589
Prost.

1712
02:04:57,027 --> 02:04:58,358
- Cognac.
- Yeah.

1713
02:05:00,530 --> 02:05:03,795
So what would you be
doing now back in Texas?

1714
02:05:05,168 --> 02:05:06,998
On Christmas morning,
we'd open our

1715
02:05:06,999 --> 02:05:08,626
presents and then go to church.

1716
02:05:09,272 --> 02:05:11,638
Then, we'd head over to
Grandma and Grandpa's...

1717
02:05:11,708 --> 02:05:13,608
for a big roast turkey dinner.

1718
02:05:14,077 --> 02:05:16,238
After that, Dad, Grandpa and me...

1719
02:05:16,913 --> 02:05:19,347
we'd go out back hunting
for pheasant, quail.

1720
02:05:20,216 --> 02:05:22,343
Hunting. Hunting was my passion.

1721
02:05:23,153 --> 02:05:25,178
I was Germany's chief gamekeeper.

1722
02:05:25,255 --> 02:05:26,279
No kidding.

1723
02:05:26,356 --> 02:05:29,291
The shooting around my estates
at Carinhall was wonderful.

1724
02:05:30,860 --> 02:05:32,725
Did Hitler ever go
hunting with you?

1725
02:05:35,532 --> 02:05:39,491
I shouldn't tell you this, but
Hitler did not approve of hunting.

1726
02:05:40,136 --> 02:05:42,661
He felt that killing
animals was immoral.

1727
02:05:43,740 --> 02:05:45,469
- He was a vegetarian.
- Yeah?

1728
02:05:45,709 --> 02:05:47,404
Yes. He was a vegetarian.

1729
02:05:49,913 --> 02:05:51,847
Yeah, but that did
not stop him from

1730
02:05:51,848 --> 02:05:53,940
being the most gracious
host in Europe.

1731
02:05:55,619 --> 02:05:57,676
His dinner parties
were legend. Always

1732
02:05:57,677 --> 02:05:59,419
the finest caviar and champagne.

1733
02:05:59,856 --> 02:06:02,791
Thought he did not partake,
he was not intolerant.

1734
02:06:03,226 --> 02:06:06,088
He would dazzle his
guests with every

1735
02:06:06,089 --> 02:06:08,425
view under the sun until dawn.

1736
02:06:10,066 --> 02:06:12,503
I remember once we
were celebrating

1737
02:06:12,504 --> 02:06:14,400
the triumph of Compiégne...

1738
02:06:15,038 --> 02:06:17,097
where we savoured the
