I share in the total
responsibility for

1986
02:20:30,577 --> 02:20:32,754
the disaster of the German people.

1987
02:20:32,828 --> 02:20:36,264
Dr Speer, near the end of the war,
did you not refuse to carry out...

1988
02:20:36,365 --> 02:20:38,925
Hitler's order to raze
Germany to the ground?

1989
02:20:39,001 --> 02:20:40,846
I've no intention
of using my actions

1990
02:20:40,847 --> 02:20:42,402
during that phase of the war...

1991
02:20:42,505 --> 02:20:44,803
to help me in my personal defence.

1992
02:20:45,474 --> 02:20:48,170
But I would like those who
sit in judgement of me...

1993
02:20:48,244 --> 02:20:49,871
to understand that period.

1994
02:20:50,713 --> 02:20:53,682
In March of 1945, Hitler
intended, deliberately...

1995
02:20:53,749 --> 02:20:56,075
to destroy the means
of life for his

1996
02:20:56,076 --> 02:20:58,152
own people if the war were lost.

1997
02:20:59,688 --> 02:21:02,748
He said, "Let the Allies
conquer nothing but ashes."

1998
02:21:03,192 --> 02:21:06,087
But you resisted his
wishes, sending

1999
02:21:06,088 --> 02:21:08,357
him instead this memorandum.

2000
02:21:08,964 --> 02:21:11,592
Would you read it to
the court, please?

2001
02:21:13,335 --> 02:21:16,964
"Nobody has the right to
destroy industrial plants...

2002
02:21:17,172 --> 02:21:21,438
"coal mines, electrical
plants, and other facilities.

2003
02:21:22,044 --> 02:21:24,375
"We have no right to
carry out destruction

2004
02:21:24,376 --> 02:21:26,708
which might affect the
life of the people.

2005
02:21:27,449 --> 02:21:29,144
"Signed, Speer."

2006
02:21:30,853 --> 02:21:33,181
We have heard here
that people were

2007
02:21:33,182 --> 02:21:35,381
shot for disagreeing with Hitler.

2008
02:21:36,859 --> 02:21:37,859
Is this true?

2009
02:21:39,028 --> 02:21:40,154
That did happen.

2010
02:21:40,229 --> 02:21:43,096
And yet, not only did you
disagree with him...

2011
02:21:43,165 --> 02:21:47,033
but early in 1945 you actually
made a plan to assassinate Hitler.

2012
02:21:47,269 --> 02:21:48,497
He what?

2013
02:21:53,943 --> 02:21:55,467
Is that not so?

2014
02:21:59,214 --> 02:22:00,306
Yes, it is so.

2015
02:22:00,382 --> 02:22:01,382
Traitor.

2016
02:22:02,751 --> 02:22:04,742
It is so...

2017
02:22:05,321 --> 02:22:08,813
because of what I viewed as
his insane destructiveness.

2018
02:22:09,825 --> 02:22:10,917
What did you do?

2019
02:22:10,993 --> 02:22:12,187
What was your plan?

2020
02:22:21,370 --> 02:22:24,533
I knew of an air-intake shaft...

2021
02:22:25,441 --> 02:22:27,989
in the Reich Chancellery
garden that

2022
02:22:27,990 --> 02:22:30,401
ventilated the Führerbunker below.

2023
02:22:31,213 --> 02:22:34,614
I went to the head of my
munitions department and said:

2024
02:22:35,918 --> 02:22:38,751
"There's only one way
to end this war."...

2025
02:22:39,622 --> 02:22:41,647
and asked him to get me...

2026
02:22:42,625 --> 02:22:46,288
a poison gas to drop into
the ventilating system.

2027
02:22:47,329 --> 02:22:48,832
But the next time I went there,

2028
02:22:48,833 --> 02:22:50,628
they had built a
12-foot chimney...

2029
02:22:50,699 --> 02:22:54,465
protecting the ventilator, and
SS guards were patrolling there.

2030
02:22:54,570 --> 02:22:57,971
So it came to nothing.

2031
02:23:05,280 --> 02:23:06,577
Mr Chief Prosecutor?

2032
02:23:09,685 --> 02:23:13,644
You acknowledge responsibility
for Germany's large policies...

2033
02:23:13,722 --> 02:23:16,384
but not for the details
occurred in their execution.

2034
02:23:16,458 --> 02:23:18,731
Is that a fair statement
of your position?

2035
02:23:18,732 --> 02:23:19,894
Yes, sir. Very fair.

2036
02:23:20,429 --> 02:23:22,177
May I ask the witness
a question in

2037
02:23:22,178 --> 02:23:24,024
order to clarify
this answer, please?

2038
02:23:24,433 --> 02:23:25,433
You may.

2039
02:23:26,969 --> 02:23:30,097
Do you want to acknowledge
guilt under criminal law...

2040
02:23:30,339 --> 02:23:33,968
or do you wish to record a
historical responsibility...

2041
02:23:34,209 --> 02:23:37,144
before your own people
and before history?

2042
02:23:49,191 --> 02:23:51,557
The question is a very
difficult one to answer.

2043
02:23:53,328 --> 02:23:57,321
It is actually one
which the Tribunal...

2044
02:23:58,534 --> 02:24:01,833
will decide in its verdict.

2045
02:24:25,027 --> 02:24:26,358
Cuffs off.

2046
02:24:27,162 --> 02:24:29,323
You would assassinate the Führer?

2047
02:24:29,631 --> 02:24:31,098
I tell you this, coward.

2048
02:24:31,166 --> 02:24:34,135
If you get out alive, we'll
put together our own court...

2049
02:24:34,203 --> 02:24:35,864
and execute you for treason.

2050
02:24:35,938 --> 02:24:36,996
Lock them up.

2051
02:24:45,214 --> 02:24:47,760
As a German officer,
I consider it my

2052
02:24:47,761 --> 02:24:50,174
duty to answer for
all I have done.

2053
02:24:51,787 --> 02:24:54,157
It will not always be
possible to separate

2054
02:24:54,158 --> 02:24:56,087
guilt from the threads of destiny.

2055
02:24:56,625 --> 02:25:00,584
But the men in the front lines
cannot be charged with guilt...

2056
02:25:00,996 --> 02:25:03,931
while the highest leaders
reject responsibility.

2057
02:25:04,700 --> 02:25:05,758
That is wrong.

2058
02:25:05,834 --> 02:25:07,631
It was my guilt...

2059
02:25:08,604 --> 02:25:11,971
which I carry before God and
the entire German nation...

2060
02:25:13,475 --> 02:25:15,296
that I educated the
youth of Germany

2061
02:25:15,297 --> 02:25:17,070
for a man who I
considered to be...

2062
02:25:17,146 --> 02:25:20,343
an impeccable leader
and head of state.

2063
02:25:21,150 --> 02:25:23,584
But I educated the
youth of Germany...

2064
02:25:24,887 --> 02:25:28,755
for a man who committed
murder a millionfold.

2065
02:25:28,824 --> 02:25:32,521
And this guilt of Germany
will not yet be erased.

2066
02:25:43,806 --> 02:25:45,467
Good afternoon, Captain.

2067
02:25:47,976 --> 02:25:49,944
The prisoners aren't
allowed visitors.

2068
02:25:50,312 --> 02:25:52,746
I am the wife of R
eichsmarschall Göring.

2069
02:25:52,881 --> 02:25:54,371
This is his daughter.

2070
02:25:55,350 --> 02:25:57,147
No exceptions, madam.

2071
02:25:58,654 --> 02:26:00,121
Frau Göring.

2072
02:26:04,092 --> 02:26:06,526
- My name is Captain Gilbert.
- Hello.

2073
02:26:06,595 --> 02:26:10,224
Nice to meet you. Would you have a
moment to spend with me, to talk?

2074
02:26:10,299 --> 02:26:11,323
Yes.

2075
02:26:11,466 --> 02:26:13,263
- Very good.
- This is Edda.

2076
02:26:13,335 --> 02:26:16,793
Hello, Edda. I'm Captain
Gilbert. Do you like chocolate?

2077
02:26:22,377 --> 02:26:25,505
It must have been very difficult
for you these last few months.

2078
02:26:25,581 --> 02:26:27,674
Especially with your little girl.

2079
02:26:27,749 --> 02:26:30,254
It could have been
worse, I suppose.

2080
02:26:30,255 --> 02:26:32,152
Hitler could have survived.

2081
02:26:33,789 --> 02:26:36,189
You've obviously come to
terms with the truth.

2082
02:26:36,825 --> 02:26:38,850
I wish your husband
could do the same.

2083
02:26:38,961 --> 02:26:42,260
But he persists in remaining
loyal to Hitler's memory.

2084
02:26:42,331 --> 02:26:45,198
Yes, I cannot
understand it, either.

2085
02:26:45,801 --> 02:26:49,396
Such loyalty to a man
who wanted us dead.

2086
02:26:50,972 --> 02:26:51,972
I'm sorry?

2087
02:26:51,973 --> 02:26:54,071
Hitler ordered all
of us to be shot.

2088
02:26:55,244 --> 02:26:56,734
Hermann, myself...

2089
02:26:56,979 --> 02:26:58,503
our precious child.

2090
02:26:59,581 --> 02:27:02,379
That is why we surrendered
to the Americans.

2091
02:27:02,484 --> 02:27:04,543
Why else would we have
done such a thing?

2092
02:27:13,161 --> 02:27:15,356
I went through my
notes last night.

2093
02:27:15,731 --> 02:27:19,497
I've spent all these months trying
to find a way inside their minds.

2094
02:27:19,568 --> 02:27:21,704
Hoping to understand
how those people

2095
02:27:21,705 --> 02:27:23,504
could commit such atrocities...

2096
02:27:23,572 --> 02:27:25,665
against my people.

2097
02:27:27,376 --> 02:27:30,971
I believe there are a couple of
factors that explain a lot of it.

2098
02:27:31,313 --> 02:27:35,147
First, Germany is a country where
people do what they're told.

2099
02:27:36,051 --> 02:27:40,283
You obey your parents, teachers,
clergymen, superior officers.

2100
02:27:40,355 --> 02:27:43,984
You're raised from childhood
not to question authority.

2101
02:27:44,493 --> 02:27:47,860
When Hitler comes to power, he has
an entire nation that believes...

2102
02:27:47,963 --> 02:27:50,761
it's perfectly natural
to do whatever he says.

2103
02:27:51,733 --> 02:27:54,031
Second, propaganda.

2104
02:27:54,836 --> 02:27:58,294
For years, Germans have been
bombarded with ideas like:

2105
02:27:58,807 --> 02:28:01,320
"Jews are not real
human beings," or

2106
02:28:01,321 --> 02:28:03,767
"They're a corruption
of the race."

2107
02:28:06,081 --> 02:28:08,799
When the government
says it's permissible

2108
02:28:08,800 --> 02:28:10,677
to deny Jews their rights...

2109
02:28:10,919 --> 02:28:16,824
and then says it's imperative to
kill these inferior people...

2110
02:28:18,760 --> 02:28:20,489
they comply.

2111
02:28:22,164 --> 02:28:25,327
Even if they've been your
friends or neighbours.

2112
02:28:32,574 --> 02:28:33,768
Anything else?

2113
02:28:33,842 --> 02:28:36,936
I told you once that I was
searching for the nature of evil.

2114
02:28:37,946 --> 02:28:40,414
I think I've come
close to defining it.

2115
02:28:41,950 --> 02:28:43,417
A lack of empathy.

2116
02:28:43,785 --> 02:28:47,516
It's the one characteristic that
connects all the defendants.

2117
02:28:47,589 --> 02:28:51,548
A genuine incapacity to
feel with their fellow man.

2118
02:28:54,162 --> 02:28:59,429
Evil, I think, is the
absence of empathy.

2119
02:29:11,580 --> 02:29:15,107
I call on the chief prosecutor
for his closing argument.

2120
02:29:24,793 --> 02:29:27,626
Mr President and members
of the tribunal.

2121
02:29:29,464 --> 02:29:31,860
It is impossible
in summation to do

2122
02:29:31,861 --> 02:29:34,458
more than outline
with bold strokes...

2123
02:29:35,037 --> 02:29:39,269
the vitals of this trial's
mad and melancholy record.

2124
02:29:39,341 --> 02:29:43,505
For no time has ever witnessed
slaughter on such a grand scale.

2125
02:29:44,746 --> 02:29:49,342
Such cruelties and inhumanities,
such wholesale deportations...

2126
02:29:50,252 --> 02:29:54,518
of peoples into slavery, such
annihilations of minorities.

2127
02:29:56,792 --> 02:30:01,252
Events which will live as
the historical text...

2128
02:30:01,329 --> 02:30:07,063
of the 20th century's
shame and depravity.

2129
02:30:07,936 --> 02:30:09,767
Terror was the order of the day.

2130
02:30:09,871 --> 02:30:11,401
Civilians were arrested without

2131
02:30:11,402 --> 02:30:13,329
charges, committed
without counsel...

2132
02:30:13,442 --> 02:30:16,309
executed without hearing.

2133
02:30:18,346 --> 02:30:21,713
Villages were destroyed, the
male inhabitants shot...

2134
02:30:23,118 --> 02:30:24,813
or sent to forced labour...

2135
02:30:24,986 --> 02:30:27,580
and the children scattered abroad.

2136
02:30:28,824 --> 02:30:31,290
The Nazi movement will
be of evil memory

2137
02:30:31,291 --> 02:30:33,818
because of its persecution
of the Jews...

2138
02:30:34,663 --> 02:30:38,258
the most far-flung and terrible
racial persecution of all time.

2139
02:30:40,035 --> 02:30:42,145
So thorough and
uncompromising was this

2140
02:30:42,146 --> 02:30:43,994
program that the Jews of Europe...

2141
02:30:44,106 --> 02:30:46,199
as a race, no longer exist.

2142
02:30:47,542 --> 02:30:49,647
Thus fulfilling the
diabolic "prophesy" of

2143
02:30:49,648 --> 02:30:51,706
Adolf Hitler at the
beginning of the war.

2144
02:30:51,780 --> 02:30:54,772
Generations to come will
remember this decade.

2145
02:30:56,051 --> 02:30:58,485
If we cannot eliminate
the cause...

2146
02:30:59,121 --> 02:31:01,919
and prevent the repetition
of these barbaric events...

2147
02:31:01,990 --> 02:31:04,151
this century may yet succeed...

2148
02:31:05,260 --> 02:31:07,660
in bringing the doom
of civilisation.

2149
02:31:10,232 --> 02:31:12,115
The time has come
for final judgement

2150
02:31:12,116 --> 02:31:14,100
and if the case I
present seems hard...

2151
02:31:14,202 --> 02:31:16,534
and uncompromising...

2152
02:31:17,172 --> 02:31:20,369
then it is only because
the evidence makes it so.

2153
02:31:21,943 --> 02:31:23,748
A glance at the
dock will show that

2154
02:31:23,749 --> 02:31:25,606
despite quarrels
among themselves...

2155
02:31:26,114 --> 02:31:29,345
each defendant played a part that
fitted in with every other...

2156
02:31:29,417 --> 02:31:31,942
and all advanced a common plan.

2157
02:31:33,788 --> 02:31:37,189
It was these men among millions of
others, and it was these men...

2158
02:31:37,325 --> 02:31:40,317
leading millions of others,
who built up Adolf Hitler.

2159
02:31:40,395 --> 02:31:41,726
They intoxicated him.

2160
02:31:41,796 --> 02:31:45,027
He, of the psychopathic
personality...

2161
02:31:45,133 --> 02:31:48,261
with power and adulation.

2162
02:31:49,771 --> 02:31:52,262
They fed his hates,
aroused his fears.

2163
02:31:53,241 --> 02:31:55,230
They put a loaded gun
in his eager hands.

2164
02:31:55,231 --> 02:31:57,268
It was left to Hitler
to pull the trigger.

2165
02:31:57,345 --> 02:31:59,279
When he did, they all...

2166
02:31:59,848 --> 02:32:02,146
at that time, applauded.

2167
02:32:03,251 --> 02:32:05,219
Hitler's guilt stands admitted...

2168
02:32:05,287 --> 02:32:07,619
by some defendants reluctantly...

2169
02:32:07,689 --> 02:32:09,554
by some, vindictively.

2170
02:32:10,125 --> 02:32:13,959
But Hitler's guilt is the
guilt of the whole dock...

2171
02:32:16,498 --> 02:32:18,523
and of every man in it.

2172
02:32:25,073 --> 02:32:27,297
These defendants now
ask this tribunal

2173
02:32:27,298 --> 02:32:29,009
to say they are not guilty...

2174
02:32:29,544 --> 02:32:32,980
of planning, executing, or
conspiring to commit...

2175
02:32:33,148 --> 02:32:37,642
this long list of
crimes and wrongs.

2176
02:32:40,589 --> 02:32:42,421
They stand before
the record of this

2177
02:32:42,422 --> 02:32:44,355
Tribunal as bloodstained
Gloucester...

2178
02:32:44,426 --> 02:32:46,951
stood by the body
of his slain king.

2179
02:32:49,197 --> 02:32:52,724
He begged the widow,
as they beg of you:

2180
02:32:54,236 --> 02:32:56,101
"Say I slew them not."

2181
02:32:57,339 --> 02:33:00,672
And the Queen replied, "Then
say they are not slain.

2182
02:33:03,345 --> 02:33:04,835
"But dead they are."

2183
02:33:06,548 --> 02:33:11,281
If you were to say of these men
that they are not guilty...

2184
02:33:12,921 --> 02:33:16,618
it would be as true to say
that there has been no war.

2185
02:33:18,460 --> 02:33:20,223
There are no slain.

2186
02:33:23,598 --> 02:33:25,498
There has been no crime.

2187
02:33:54,429 --> 02:33:55,657
Captain.

2188
02:33:56,631 --> 02:34:00,658
"Jews escalate fight for
homeland." It's ironic.

2189
02:34:01,803 --> 02:34:04,271
After all that's happened
over the past 10 years...

2190
02:34:04,339 --> 02:34:06,773
I don't blame the Jews
for wanting a homeland.

2191
02:34:06,841 --> 02:34:10,607
One of the many ripples we'll see
from this war and from this trial.

2192
02:34:11,913 --> 02:34:13,904
- Shall we?
- Yeah.

2193
02:34:15,116 --> 02:34:17,983
The defendants may now make
their final statements.

2194
02:34:18,920 --> 02:34:20,911
Defendant Hermann Göring.

2195
02:34:35,303 --> 02:34:38,033
This has been a poor
excuse for a trial.

2196
02:34:41,409 --> 02:34:44,776
But firstly, I must reiterate
my lack of knowledge...

2197
02:34:45,046 --> 02:34:47,588
for these terrible
mass murders, which

2198
02:34:47,589 --> 02:34:49,676
I cannot begin to understand...

2199
02:34:50,585 --> 02:34:54,919
and furthermore, I
condemn wholeheartedly.

2200
02:34:55,957 --> 02:34:57,967
As to the trial, the
statements of the

2201
02:34:57,968 --> 02:34:59,825
defendants were
accepted as true...

2202
02:34:59,928 --> 02:35:02,556
only when they supported
the prosecution.

2203
02:35:03,298 --> 02:35:06,426
They were treated as perjury when
they refuted the indictment.

2204
02:35:06,835 --> 02:35:09,030
This is not a basis of proof.

2205
02:35:09,170 --> 02:35:13,231
Why am I in the dock being
treated as a common criminal?

2206
02:35:15,076 --> 02:35:18,671
I say to my judges,
have no illusions.

2207
02:35:19,547 --> 02:35:21,653
Since the three greatest
powers on earth,

2208
02:35:21,654 --> 02:35:23,711
together with other
nations fought us...

2209
02:35:23,785 --> 02:35:28,347
we finally were conquered by
tremendous enemy superiority.

2210
02:35:28,857 --> 02:35:33,487
Justice has absolutely nothing
to do with this trial.

2211
02:35:47,475 --> 02:35:49,534
Defendant Albert Speer.

2212
02:35:54,416 --> 02:35:59,251
How could so advanced,
so cultured...

2213
02:36:00,422 --> 02:36:03,289
so sophisticated a
nation as Germany...

2214
02:36:04,058 --> 02:36:06,720
have fallen under
Hitler's demonic sway?

2215
02:36:07,962 --> 02:36:11,090
The explanation is
modern communications.

2216
02:36:12,400 --> 02:36:14,787
No longer does a leader
have to delegate

2217
02:36:14,788 --> 02:36:16,769
authority afar to subordinates...

2218
02:36:17,105 --> 02:36:19,369
exercising independent judgement.

2219
02:36:19,774 --> 02:36:22,060
Given modern
communications, a Hitler

2220
02:36:22,061 --> 02:36:24,108
can rule directly and personally.

2221
02:36:25,079 --> 02:36:28,014
Thus, the more technical
the world becomes...

2222
02:36:28,216 --> 02:36:30,844
the more individual freedom...

2223
02:36:31,286 --> 02:36:34,153
and the self-rule of
mankind becomes essential.

2224
02:36:35,690 --> 02:36:40,855
This war has ended on the note
of radio-controlled rockets.

2225
02:36:41,830 --> 02:36:44,230
Aircraft approaching
the speed of sound.

2226
02:36:44,466 --> 02:36:47,560
Submarines and torpedoes which
can find their own targets.

2227
02:36:47,669 --> 02:36:49,000
Atom bombs...

2228
02:36:49,237 --> 02:36:52,172
and the horrible prospect
of chemical warfare.

2229
02:36:52,607 --> 02:36:55,048
In five to ten years,
this kind of warfare will

2230
02:36:55,049 --> 02:36:57,237
offer the possibility
of firing rockets...

2231
02:36:57,312 --> 02:37:00,748
from continent to continent
with uncanny precision.

2232
02:37:01,983 --> 02:37:04,076
Through the smashing
of the atom...

2233
02:37:05,119 --> 02:37:07,352
it will be possible to
kill 1 million people

2234
02:37:07,353 --> 02:37:09,488
in New York City in a
matter of seconds...

2235
02:37:09,557 --> 02:37:12,321
with a rocket serviced
by perhaps ten men.

2236
02:37:14,028 --> 02:37:18,431
A new large-scale war will
end with the destruction...

2237
02:37:18,566 --> 02:37:21,160
of human culture and civilisation.

2238
02:37:21,503 --> 02:37:24,529
That is why this trial
must contribute...

2239
02:37:25,440 --> 02:37:28,238
to the prevention of
such wars in the future.

2240
02:37:30,078 --> 02:37:33,514
A nation believing in its
future will never perish.

2241
02:37:34,182 --> 02:37:37,811
May God protect Germany...

2242
02:37:39,587 --> 02:37:41,578
and the culture of the West.

2243
02:37:51,432 --> 02:37:53,845
We are agreed. Three
of four votes will

2244
02:37:53,846 --> 02:37:56,199
be required for the
finding of guilty.

2245
02:37:56,971 --> 02:37:58,268
- Agreed.
- Agreed.

2246
02:37:58,406 --> 02:38:02,365
Now, if the judgement is death,
might we not consider...

2247
02:38:02,443 --> 02:38:05,173
the firing squad for the
military defendants?

2248
02:38:05,246 --> 02:38:07,009
I disagree most strongly.

2249
02:38:07,148 --> 02:38:10,515
The bullet is for the honourable
adversary, not for butchers.

2250
02:38:11,486 --> 02:38:12,919
I say hanging.

2251
02:38:13,321 --> 02:38:14,982
- I agree.
- I agree.

2252
02:38:18,059 --> 02:38:21,460
We will take the defendants in
the order they were indicted.

2253
02:38:21,729 --> 02:38:22,729
Göring.

2254
02:38:31,039 --> 02:38:32,597
Bravo.

2255
02:38:43,117 --> 02:38:45,551
Go on, have some of
the lovely food.

2256
02:38:50,291 --> 02:38:53,021
There is talk that you
will all be hanged.

2257
02:38:53,828 --> 02:38:55,261
I won't be hanged.

2258
02:38:56,831 --> 02:39:00,494
That I assure you. That I pledge.

2259
02:39:02,070 --> 02:39:06,097
Perhaps the court will send
you to an island, like Elba.

2260
02:39:07,008 --> 02:39:09,033
We could join you there.

2261
02:39:13,581 --> 02:39:15,071
Go on, eat.

2262
02:39:17,952 --> 02:39:20,304
Do you think that
we would be allowed

2263
02:39:20,305 --> 02:39:22,719
to take some of the
food home with us?

2264
02:39:29,998 --> 02:39:31,761
I don't see why not.

2265
02:39:32,800 --> 02:39:35,769
The Charter clearly states
that following orders...

2266
02:39:36,304 --> 02:39:39,569
"may be considered in
mitigation of punishment."

2267
02:39:40,008 --> 02:39:42,340
"May be," not must be.

2268
02:39:46,547 --> 02:39:50,643
You have become such
beautiful young ladies.

2269
02:39:55,957 --> 02:39:57,982
When are they going
to shoot you, Papa?

2270
02:39:59,560 --> 02:40:01,892
Hans Frank is a most
tragic figure...

2271
02:40:02,130 --> 02:40:03,154
in my view.

2272
02:40:03,231 --> 02:40:05,290
His penitence is obviously real.

2273
02:40:05,833 --> 02:40:09,064
It would be a meaningful gesture
for us to spare his life.

2274
02:40:09,936 --> 02:40:10,936
No.

2275
02:40:10,938 --> 02:40:11,996
He should hang.

2276
02:40:51,145 --> 02:40:52,806
Atten-hut.

2277
02:40:57,885 --> 02:40:59,147
All rise.

2278
02:41:38,326 --> 02:41:42,023
Each defendant will stand
as his name is called...

2279
02:41:42,330 --> 02:41:45,891
to hear the judgements on the
four counts applicable to him...

2280
02:41:46,634 --> 02:41:50,195
and the sentence, if found
guilty on any of the counts.

2281
02:41:51,172 --> 02:41:54,733
The counts, numbered
one through four, are:

2282
02:41:55,543 --> 02:41:57,977
Conspiracy to commit aggression.

2283
02:41:58,713 --> 02:42:00,647
The commission of aggression.

2284
02:42:01,516 --> 02:42:03,882
Crimes in the conduct
of warfare...

2285
02:42:04,519 --> 02:42:06,510
and crimes against humanity.

2286
02:42:07,755 --> 02:42:09,780
Defendant Hermann Göring.

2287
02:42:14,862 --> 02:42:18,821
The Tribunal finds you
guilty on all four counts...

2288
02:42:19,267 --> 02:42:20,734
and sentences you...

2289
02:42:21,102 --> 02:42:22,763
to death by hanging.

2290
02:42:26,974 --> 02:42:28,373
Rudolf Hess.

2291
02:42:30,111 --> 02:42:32,636
On the charges of crimes
against humanity...

2292
02:42:32,914 --> 02:42:35,178
the Tribunal finds you not guilty.

2293
02:42:35,917 --> 02:42:38,909
But we find you guilty
on counts one and two...

2294
02:42:39,520 --> 02:42:43,081
and thereby sentence you
to imprisonment for life.

2295
02:42:44,659 --> 02:42:46,559
Admiral Wilhelm Keitel.

2296
02:42:47,361 --> 02:42:49,261
Guilty on all four counts.

2297
02:42:49,664 --> 02:42:52,462
The Tribunal sentences
you to death by hanging.

2298
02:42:53,935 --> 02:42:55,835
Defendant Hans Frank.

2299
02:42:57,338 --> 02:43:00,865
The Tribunal finds you guilty
on counts three and four...

2300
02:43:01,642 --> 02:43:04,042
and sentences you to
death by hanging.

2301
02:43:04,278 --> 02:43:05,905
Julius Streicher.

2302
02:43:07,348 --> 02:43:10,613
Guilty on count four,
crimes against humanity.

2303
02:43:11,352 --> 02:43:12,478
Death by hanging.

2304
02:43:13,120 --> 02:43:14,781
Defendant Schacht.

2305
02:43:15,556 --> 02:43:18,224
The Tribunal has come
to the conclusion

2306
02:43:18,225 --> 02:43:20,960
that evidence against
Hjalmar Schacht...

2307
02:43:21,529 --> 02:43:24,498
has not been established
beyond a reasonable doubt...

2308
02:43:24,632 --> 02:43:28,625
and therefore finds that Schacht
is not guilty on this indictment.

2309
02:43:30,938 --> 02:43:32,030
Quiet, please.

2310
02:43:36,043 --> 02:43:38,136
The Defendant Karl Dönitz.

2311
02:43:38,846 --> 02:43:40,837
Guilty on counts two and three.

2312
02:43:41,482 --> 02:43:45,213
The Tribunal sentences you
to ten years imprisonment.

2313
02:43:46,888 --> 02:43:49,220
Foreign Minister von Ribbentrop.

2314
02:43:50,091 --> 02:43:52,218
Guilty on all four counts.

2315
02:43:52,627 --> 02:43:55,528
The Tribunal sentences
you to death by hanging.

2316
02:43:58,165 --> 02:43:59,792
Ernst Kaltenbrunner.

2317
02:44:00,668 --> 02:44:02,636
Guilty on counts three and four.

2318
02:44:03,671 --> 02:44:06,572
The Tribunal sentences
you to death by hanging.

2319
02:44:06,741 --> 02:44:08,402
Balder von Schirach.

2320
02:44:08,809 --> 02:44:10,902
Guilty on count four.

2321
02:44:11,178 --> 02:44:12,702
Twenty years in prison.

2322
02:44:12,780 --> 02:44:13,906
Alfred Jodl.

2323
02:44:14,348 --> 02:44:16,407
On all four counts, guilty.

2324
02:44:17,051 --> 02:44:18,177
Death by hanging.

2325
02:44:19,053 --> 02:44:20,543
Hans Fritzsche.

2326
02:44:22,657 --> 02:44:24,022
Not guilty.

2327
02:44:26,060 --> 02:44:27,652
Franz von Papen.

2328
02:44:29,630 --> 02:44:30,995
Not guilty.

2329
02:44:32,199 --> 02:44:33,199
Walter Funk.

2330
02:44:34,068 --> 02:44:36,002
Guilty on counts
two, three and four.

2331
02:44:36,637 --> 02:44:39,936
The Tribunal sentences you
to imprisonment for life.

2332
02:44:40,574 --> 02:44:42,542
Defendant Fritz Sauckel.

2333
02:44:43,511 --> 02:44:45,775
Guilty on counts three and four.

2334
02:44:46,314 --> 02:44:47,440
Death by hanging.

2335
02:44:49,383 --> 02:44:51,044
Defendant Albert Speer.

2336
02:44:53,120 --> 02:44:56,647
The Tribunal finds you not
guilty on counts one and two.

2337
02:44:57,491 --> 02:45:01,018
But you have been found guilty
on counts three and four.

2338
02:45:01,595 --> 02:45:03,825
Albert Speer, the Court
sentences you...

2339
02:45:03,898 --> 02:45:06,162
to 20 years imprisonment.

2340
02:45:12,673 --> 02:45:15,665
The work of this Tribunal
is now complete.

2341
02:46:34,722 --> 02:46:36,212
Lock them up.

2342
02:46:42,463 --> 02:46:45,796
Leutnant, my dear Tex,
why this long face?

2343
02:46:47,134 --> 02:46:48,976
Have I not told you
there's a special

2344
02:46:48,977 --> 02:46:50,626
place in Valhalla waiting for me?

2345
02:46:53,174 --> 02:46:54,641
I don't know.

2346
02:47:00,347 --> 02:47:02,815
I thought things might have
turned out differently.

2347
02:47:03,184 --> 02:47:05,648
Well, you know, they
might have done,

2348
02:47:05,649 --> 02:47:08,178
if it wasn't a very
unfortunate thing.

2349
02:47:10,157 --> 02:47:11,624
Those mass murders.

2350
02:47:12,893 --> 02:47:15,623
I must tell you, I could
not see their purpose.

2351
02:47:15,696 --> 02:47:17,994
They were absolutely unnecessary.

2352
02:47:18,065 --> 02:47:20,693
They made no sense from a
nationalistic point of view.

2353
02:47:20,868 --> 02:47:23,336
Our legacy has been
forever tainted.

2354
02:47:25,005 --> 02:47:26,529
But make no mistake.

2355
02:47:27,475 --> 02:47:29,298
Everything Hitler
did before the war

2356
02:47:29,299 --> 02:47:31,172
was right. The German
people knew it.

2357
02:47:31,245 --> 02:47:32,974
One day, they'll remember it.

2358
02:47:33,080 --> 02:47:35,878
And you must remember
it too, my dear Tex.

2359
02:47:37,084 --> 02:47:39,484
When you remember
me, remember that.

2360
02:47:41,622 --> 02:47:42,622
Yeah.

2361
02:47:44,158 --> 02:47:46,023
Now, to practical matters.

2362
02:47:47,027 --> 02:47:49,074
There are a few things
I want to give you.

2363
02:47:49,075 --> 02:47:50,075
No, sir...

2364
02:47:50,331 --> 02:47:51,389
Please.

2365
02:47:54,835 --> 02:47:57,429
Where I'm going, I
must travel light.

2366
02:48:00,941 --> 02:48:04,206
It's inscribed, see,
with my name. Take it.

2367
02:48:05,980 --> 02:48:07,208
Take it.

2368
02:48:15,289 --> 02:48:17,377
The few valuables I
have, they are in

2369
02:48:17,378 --> 02:48:19,521
my blue briefcase in
the baggage room.

2370
02:48:19,593 --> 02:48:22,426
Can you retrieve that
for me, my dear Tex?

2371
02:48:24,198 --> 02:48:25,198
Yes, sir.

2372
02:48:57,798 --> 02:49:00,198
Where are they building
those gallows?

2373
02:49:00,301 --> 02:49:02,826
Down in the back. Third
building on the right.

2374
02:49:31,498 --> 02:49:34,023
I have only one
question to ask you.

2375
02:49:35,769 --> 02:49:37,760
Is there absolutely
no possibility that I

2376
02:49:37,761 --> 02:49:39,705
may be allowed to face
a firing squad...

2377
02:49:39,773 --> 02:49:41,400
and die a soldier's death?

2378
02:49:41,475 --> 02:49:42,475
None.

2379
02:49:43,444 --> 02:49:47,107
Just as well. I hear the
Americans are very poor shots.

2380
02:49:48,983 --> 02:49:51,747
Now, if you'll excuse me,
I must write a letter.

2381
02:50:02,329 --> 02:50:05,093
For the rest of my life,
Herr Reichsmarschall...

2382
02:50:05,466 --> 02:50:08,026
people will ask me what
your final thoughts were.

2383
02:50:08,235 --> 02:50:10,032
I'll have nothing to tell them.

2384
02:50:10,137 --> 02:50:11,832
You can tell them this:

2385
02:50:13,140 --> 02:50:15,074
I say, for now and all time:

2386
02:50:16,143 --> 02:50:18,347
The foreigners who
have imposed this

2387
02:50:18,348 --> 02:50:20,375
sentence upon me may murder me...

2388
02:50:20,481 --> 02:50:23,109
but they have no
right to judge me.

2389
02:50:23,684 --> 02:50:25,675
That I deny them.

2390
02:50:27,688 --> 02:50:32,148
Now, you must excuse me, I do have
to write this letter. Thank you.

2391
02:50:40,501 --> 02:50:42,594
My one and only sweetheart.

2392
02:50:42,936 --> 02:50:46,565
My life came to an end when I bade
you farewell for the last time.

2393
02:50:47,341 --> 02:50:49,241
Do not grieve, my dearest one.

2394
02:50:49,643 --> 02:50:52,314
Since then I have felt
at peace with myself,

2395
02:50:52,315 --> 02:50:54,512
and consider my death
a deliverance.

2396
02:50:55,749 --> 02:50:59,446
All my thoughts are with you
and our own dear, sweet child.

2397
02:51:00,521 --> 02:51:04,423
My last heartbeats, of our
great and eternal love.

2398
02:51:57,611 --> 02:51:59,135
Colonel, may I?

2399
02:52:02,883 --> 02:52:04,942
- You got what you want?
- I got it, sir.

2400
02:52:05,152 --> 02:52:06,949
Gentlemen, follow me.

2401
02:52:36,450 --> 02:52:37,644
Mein Gott.

2402
02:52:39,086 --> 02:52:40,485
Get dressed.

2403
02:53:05,012 --> 02:53:06,479
Get a doctor.

2404
02:53:08,148 --> 02:53:10,013
Somebody get a doctor.

2405
02:53:46,220 --> 02:53:47,448
Cyanide.

2406
02:54:11,745 --> 02:54:13,372
Son of a bitch.

2407
02:54:44,978 --> 02:54:48,470
- State your name.
- Joachim von Ribbentrop.

2408
02:54:48,916 --> 02:54:50,781
Do you have anything to say?

2409
02:54:51,018 --> 02:54:54,419
My last wish is that Germany
realise its destiny.

2410
02:54:55,188 --> 02:54:57,213
I wish peace to the world.

2411
02:55:16,310 --> 02:55:19,939
- Do you have anything to say?
- I now join my sons.

2412
02:55:20,914 --> 02:55:23,382
Deutschland über alles.

2413
02:55:45,272 --> 02:55:46,398
Three.

2414
02:55:52,312 --> 02:55:54,337
I'm dying an innocent man.

2415
02:55:59,720 --> 02:56:02,450
I ask God to accept
me with my sin.

2416
02:56:06,760 --> 02:56:07,760
Heil Hitler.

2417
02:56:07,828 --> 02:56:08,828
Heil Hitler.

2418
02:56:18,505 --> 02:56:19,529
Seven.

2419
02:56:47,367 --> 02:56:49,096
All cleaned out. Everything.

2420
02:56:49,803 --> 02:56:53,830
The cells are to be scrubbed
clean. Nothing's to be left.

2421
02:56:57,344 --> 02:56:58,675
Nothing.

2422
02:57:02,983 --> 02:57:04,177
Thank you very much.

2423
02:57:05,919 --> 02:57:06,919
Thanks.

2424
02:57:07,621 --> 02:57:10,681
You know, when we get home, we've
got some decisions to make.

2425
02:57:10,791 --> 02:57:13,316
Some personal decisions.

2426
02:57:14,661 --> 02:57:16,754
Let's just wait till we get home.

2427
02:57:22,102 --> 02:57:23,592
Hello, you two.

2428
02:57:24,404 --> 02:57:26,338
You know it may sound strange...

2429
02:57:26,406 --> 02:57:29,432
but I can't help feeling a touch
sentimental about all this.

2430
02:57:29,876 --> 02:57:31,343
I understand.

2431
02:57:32,679 --> 02:57:35,315
I got a letter from a
friend today saying

2432
02:57:35,316 --> 02:57:37,514
that because of what we've done...

2433
02:57:39,052 --> 02:57:40,952
none of it can ever happen again.

2434
02:57:42,489 --> 02:57:43,717
What do you think?

2435
02:57:44,958 --> 02:57:46,619
Well...

2436
02:57:48,729 --> 02:57:50,026
We can hope, can't we?

2437
02:57:55,368 --> 02:57:56,426
'Bye.

